01:39:01.701 --> 01:39:03.138
It's fallen off me.

01:39:03.394 --> 01:39:05.016
Ooh, I'm so sorry.

01:39:05.095 --> 01:39:06.586
It's very hard
to tell sometimes.

01:39:07.306 --> 01:39:08.329
Um...

01:39:08.488 --> 01:39:10.254
Secrets nobody tells.

01:39:11.774 --> 01:39:17.048
